data.description: A remarkable townhome nestled in the desirable Stoney Brook Community of Summit. With 2 beds and 1.5 baths, this home is move-in ready with a blend of comfort and convenience. Modern kitchen equipped with stainless-steel refrigerator, stove, dishwasher and new counters. Newer flooring throughout the main level. The attached garage offers additional depth, providing ample storage in addition to the reserved parking space and guest parking. A private outdoor patio opens to a grass lawn with a greenbelt view. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet. Just minutes to restaurants and shops. Convenient access to freeways. Don't miss this chance to own a townhome that combines comfort and convenience. VA approved condominium complex.
